---
title: Tex-Mex Turkey Tacos with carrot slaw and roasted pepper
description: These assemble-yourself-tacos are sure to be a hit. They've got the DIY element despite being super easy to make. Chipotle-coated turkey mince is an unexpected element to this Mexican-inspired dish.
